title: #139 - ProJared Finally Responds & Dave Chappelle Cancelled
description: On this episode of the H3 Podcast we discuss ProJared still being a creep, Dave Chappelle (not) being cancelled, we make Zach eat a bucket of mayonnaise, Hila fat shames Ethan, and we are blessed by another Bradberry instant classic!
